    "According to different cultures and characteristics of drivers, the corresponding emotional regulation methods should be explored.",
    "• Driver emotion regulation from the V2X: Because driver characteristics play an important role in emotion regula-tion, driver emotion regulation needs to consider a large amount of historical characteristics data (e.g., human driving habits, health history, and personalized preferences).",
    "By integrating the driver's social background and historical information collected from the V2X, the vehicle's emotion regulation system can ensure that appropriate regulation strategies are provided in time according to different driving contexts.",
    "• Privacy: With the rapid development of CAVs, in future scenarios, the vehicle will become a relaxed and social interaction environment (e.g., a living room or a workplace).",
    "How to respect the privacy of the occupants in the vehicle while detecting and regulating emotions will be a vital research topic."
